<p><b>What is a construction machine?</b> Construction machinery entails all machinery used for activities in construction, ranging from soil excavation to the transportation, loading, and unloading of materials and waste management.</p>
<p><b>What type of equipment is used in construction?</b> What Equipment Is Used In Construction? There are various types of equipment used in construction. Commonly used equipment is bulldozers, backhoe loaders, excavators, cranes, concrete mixers, and dumpers.</p>
